PS C:\> Set-AzDataLakeAnalyticsCatalogItemAclEntry -Account "contosoadla" -User -ObjectId (Get-AzADUser -Mail "PattiFuller@contoso.com").Id -Permissions Read
Type Id Permissions ---- -- ----------- User 90a6f74b-fd73-490e-900a-c4f0f9694d02 Read Group 902b155a-5601-4ca8-8178-ad3289211f88 ReadWrite Other 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 None User bd0b55bb-3a57-442a-b2f6-78c95c10ef86 Read

dev:remarks.maml:para: This command modifies the catalog ACE for Patti Fuller to have read permissions.

PS C:\> Set-AzDataLakeAnalyticsCatalogItemAclEntry -Account "contosoadla" -User -ObjectId (Get-AzADUser -Mail "PattiFuller@contoso.com").Id -ItemType Database -Path "databaseName" -Permissions Read
Type Id Permissions ---- -- ----------- User 90a6f74b-fd73-490e-900a-c4f0f9694d02 Read Group 902b155a-5601-4ca8-8178-ad3289211f88 ReadWrite Other 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 None User bd0b55bb-3a57-442a-b2f6-78c95c10ef86 Read

dev:remarks.maml:para: This command modifies the database ACE for Patti Fuller to have read permissions.

PS C:\> Set-AzDataLakeAnalyticsCatalogItemAclEntry -Account "contosoadla" -Other -Permissions Read
Type Id Permissions ---- -- ----------- User 90a6f74b-fd73-490e-900a-c4f0f9694d02 Read Group 902b155a-5601-4ca8-8178-ad3289211f88 ReadWrite Other 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 Read User bd0b55bb-3a57-442a-b2f6-78c95c10ef86 Read

dev:remarks.maml:para: This command modifies the catalog ACE for other to have read permissions.

Type Id Permissions ---- -- ----------- User 90a6f74b-fd73-490e-900a-c4f0f9694d02 Read Group 902b155a-5601-4ca8-8178-ad3289211f88 ReadWrite Other 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 Read User bd0b55bb-3a57-442a-b2f6-78c95c10ef86 Read
